General.Name: Careteq Limited
General.Description: Careteq Limited, a health-tech company, provides software as a service (SaaS) technology solution for health and aged care sectors worldwide. The company develops and commercializes a suite of products that sit on its proprietary SaaS based assistive living technology platform for use by the elderly, disabled, and vulnerable individuals. It also offers assistive living products and medication management services, which include expert geriatric clinical pharmacy decision support services to GPs. The company was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Melbourne, Australia.
